CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Beauty Health Co is a category-creating beauty health company focused on bringing innovative products to market. The company's flagship brand HydraFacial is a non-invasive, and approachable beauty health platform and ecosystem with a powerful community of estheticians, consumers and partners, bridging medical and consumer retail to democratize and personalize skin care solutions for the masses. Geographically, it derives a majority of revenue from the Americas.
